# 2025-11-22 15:19:58.802700
+The flip card logic is not right.
+
+Salamat shows on one side of card
+
+When you flip it, don’t show Salamat backyards, you should translate it and show Thank you, on the other side of the card. Do this for common words. They need to type answer in somewhere, then flip card to see if they get it right.  If wrong they lose a life (of 3 total). If right highlight it green for a second and move to next question  

